      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk 3.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic titanium alloy material model is appropriate for the sub-yield loading regime of the F1717 protocol. Frictional contact (mu=0.3) between screw-rod interface captures load transfer mechanism. Geometric nonlinearity enabled to account for large-displacement effects at the rod."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
