      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk 3.",
      "rationale": "Material properties (E=114 GPa, nu=0.34 for Ti-6Al-4V) sourced from ASTM F136 certified material test reports for the specific lot used in physical testing. Geometry derived from CMM measurements of actual test specimens with tolerance analysis."
    },
    {
