      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk 3.",
      "rationale": "N=11 physical constructs tested across two independent laboratories (FDA CDRH and university partner). Samples are production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws from the commercial device family. Dimensional inspection confirmed conformance to design drawings."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
