      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk 3.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single compressive offset load condition per ASTM F1717. Variation across loading rates and offset distances not explored. This factor falls below the required level and constitutes a known gap in the validation evidence base."
    },
    {
