      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk 3.",
      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate the F1717 fixture geometry including block embedment depth and loading pin position. Fixture compliance characterised experimentally and incorporated into the model. Correspondence between physical and computational setup verified by overlay comparison."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
